@node MAIN
@title "Magnify docs - ©1995 Iain King"

  Magnify is a WB 'toy', that is, it serves no constructive purpose, 
except if you are lucky enough to have a very high res monitor, and 
are unlucky enough to have bad eyesight.


        Contents:
                
                @{" How do I use Magnify? " link HOWUSE}
                @{" What other stuff does it do? " link FEATURES}
                @{" Problems? " link PROBS}
                @{" Version list " link VERS}
                @{" Future for Magnify " link FUTURE}
                @{" Credits " link INFO}

  Any damage caused by this program is nothing to do with me - I'm 
not responsible.  Magnify is Freeware, and you can pass it around as 
much as you want to your mates (please do), and you are Free to send 
